headline: Why Morgan Stanley's CIO thinks the latest volatility in stocks is making the 2026 outlook more bullish
summary: The Fed will need to respond to the market's "tantrum," Morgan Stanley's CIO said. He added that any volatility should be viewed as an opportunity.
